
## Sample API Requests (`sample_requests.http`)

```http
### Shorten URL
POST http://localhost:5000/api/shorten
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://example.com/very/long/url/to/be/shortened",
  "expiration_days": 30
}

### Get Analytics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/analytics/abc123

### Redirect (Note: This would actually be accessed in browser)
GET http://localhost:5000/abc123
